00:00:36.436 --> 00:00:38.304 line:5%,start
ABBY: <i>Let's go, girls. Come on.</i>

00:00:38.371 --> 00:00:40.273 line:95%,end
Come on. Get in here.
Come on. Come on. Come on.

00:00:43.877 --> 00:00:46.246 line:95%,end
Last week's competition,
Fire and Ice, to me,

00:00:46.312 --> 00:00:48.248 line:95%,end
was a big disappointment, ladies.

00:00:48.314 --> 00:00:50.483 line:95%,end
I mean, here we are,
invited back as winners,

